metadata.name: The Drag # 2
metadata.description: The Drag. A combination of sarcasm of modern life-style and decorated, delicate surrealism. Talented authors have created digital art pieces of 22 topics: Fantasy, Toys, Miniature, Video Game, Comic, Cartoon, Movie Set, Comedy, Medieval, Roman, Adventure, Covid, Medical, Spooky, War, Underwater, Samurai, Other, Star Wars, Apocalypse, Dystopian, Sci-Fi, Space, Abstract, Otherworldly. Each piece sold will generate a unique symbol created by algorithm and eventually make a social digital artwork.
